Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「离开我…」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是个善良并且坚强的孩子
