Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.98,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底在想什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.24,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她…  观铃怎么办！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:18.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别太接近她的话  也就不会发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.18,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}等等
