Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.06,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么  醒着呢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  刚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.57,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我听到了妈妈的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.53,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  说是出去一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我非常喜欢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:22.76,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.02,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}慢慢走  不用勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:32.89,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.90,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:44.49,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.76,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:49.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V～
