Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.19,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海有这么遥远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.00,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了
