Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.89,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.14,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又要发作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.23,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.41,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一会儿就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.98,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海…  明天再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}平静下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:32.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:35.34,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐
