Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.21,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才的表演非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}既有趣  又可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.29,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谢谢啦  一直陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就加油吧  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.25,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.22,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哪里都不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪在你身边  让你一直欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.16,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我找到窍门了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.68,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这回的表演一定很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以你要仔细看哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:43.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:47.75,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看啊！ 你笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.28,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么我一直都没注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.36,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:05.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看着你的笑容就是我要追求的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就是我要追求的幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我哪里都不会去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.37,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在我的身边欢笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:15.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐…  观铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:22.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:24.75,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你现在一定要想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.62,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自己必须做的事
