Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你回来看我了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:02.00,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看  我又恢复健康了啊
